            <title>[SPARK-14981] CatalogTable should contain sorting directions of sorting columns</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-14981</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For a bucketed table with sorting columns, &lt;tt&gt;CatalogTable&lt;/tt&gt; only records sorting column names, while sorting directions (ASC/DESC) are missing.&lt;/p&gt;

